The Nelspruit SPCA is starting its fundraising back up by selling pancakes until October 2. The organisation said it will sell the pancakes at R5 each. Here is how you can order: ALSO READ: The Nelspruit Police Station is hit by another case of Covid-19 1. Order the pancakes via WhatsApp on 083-375-44252. If you order today by 15:00, you can collect your order from the SPCA the next day from 13:003. Payment can be made at the SPCA with cash or card4. The last day to place orders is Friday.